  • Uses of BitSet in com.shouldis.bitset

    Subclasses of BitSet in com.shouldis.bitset 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ConcurrentBitSet
    Implementation of BitSet in which all methods capable of reading or writing the state of bits such as ConcurrentBitSet.setWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.andWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.orWord(int, long), ConcurrentBitSet.xOrWord(int, long) are delegated to atomic-operations.
    Methods in com.shouldis.bitset with parameters of type BitSet 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void BitSet.and​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global AND operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
    void BitSet.copy​(BitSet set)
    Transforms this BitSet so that each bit matches the state of that in the give set.
    void BitSet.not​(BitSet set)
    Transforms this BitSet into the complement of the specified set.
    void BitSet.notAnd​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global NOT AND operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
    void BitSet.notOr​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global NOT OR operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
    void BitSet.notXOr​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global NOT XOR operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
    void BitSet.or​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global OR operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
    void BitSet.xOr​(BitSet set)
    Performs a global XOR operation on all bits in this BitSet with those in the specified BitSet set.
